At 0.1.9 THIS GEM IS SHOPIFY-READ-ONLY!

Example Usage:

  Shopify.setup('store_name', 'api-key', 'api-secret', 'auth-token')

	Shopify.shop
  # => gets your shop's details/configuration
	Shopify.products
  # => gets your products
	order = Shopify.orders(:limit => 1)[0]
  # => gets first order
  order.line_items
  # => the line items within that order
